question: Sophia is required to submit a 68-page report. She already finished writing 1/2 of the report. How many pages does she have left to write?
answer:
Sophia has already written 1/2 of the report which is 68 pages*1/2 = <<68*1/2=34>>34 pages.
So, she still needs to write 68 pages - 34 pages = <<68-34=34>>34 pages.
#### 34
